FRANCE: Bangladesh to seek 100,000 tns wheat - traders.Bangladesh to seek 100,000 tns wheat - traders.Bangladesh has signalled it will tap world markets with a tender at the end of August for 100,000 tonnes of optional-origin soft wheat for shipment in September and October, European grain traders said on Monday.Although there was some market confusion over whether the import would be routine business or food aid, traders said the tender appeared to be a commercial one.Earlier this month the European Union sold 75,000 tonnes of soft wheat as food aid for delivery to Bangladesh from mid-October.--Paris newsroom +331 4221 5432